      "description": "Rivan Industries is a UK-based synthetic fuel startup that vertically integrates every step of production — from renewable energy generation and green hydrogen, to direct-air-capture CO2 and Sabatier-reactor methane synthesis — to produce Synthetic Natural Gas (SNG) for injection into the gas grid. Its primary customers are heavy industries that are hard to electrify at scale, including steel, cement, chemicals and aviation. Founded in 2024 by Harvey Hodd, the company designs and manufactures its hardware in the UK from scratch and aims to reach fossil-fuel-competitive pricing within the next 2-3 years.",
