      "description": "Companion.energy is a Ghent, Belgium-based software company, founded in 2022, that helps large industrial and commercial enterprises manage and optimize energy in real time. Its platform unifies energy contracts, operational systems, and distributed assets (solar, wind, batteries, electric boilers and EV charging) into a single optimization layer that continuously forecasts demand, models market exposure, and autonomously executes energy decisions. It serves enterprises such as TotalEnergies, KPN, the Port of Antwerp-Bruges and Proximus Group, managing over 2 TWh of annual energy use across customer portfolios.",
